                "invention-title": [
                    "Electro-hydrogen system flexibility measuring method considering space-time performance",
                    "一种考虑时空表现的电氢系统灵活性测度方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "A method for measuring the flexibility of an electro-hydrogen system considering space-time performance comprises the following steps: (1) research on flexible resources of the electro-hydrogen system: summarizing the existing research on the flexibility of the electro-hydrogen system from four aspects of flexibility resource integration, planning configuration, operation regulation and control and quantitative evaluation; (2) aiming at the uncertainty in the electro-hydrogen system, analyzing the flexibility source of the system; (3) excavating adjustable flexible resources of subunits such as energy storage, a converter, an electrolytic cell and an auxiliary machine in the system on different spatial and temporal scales on the basis of output characteristics, power adjustment and other characteristics of the electro-hydrogen system, providing a time-space-expression three-dimensional flexibility measurement system, and performing quantitative analysis on the flexibility of the electro-hydrogen system; and (4) constructing a system flexibility measurement function, depicting the flexibility of the electro-hydrogen subsystem, evaluating the flexible adjustment potential of each subsystem in the electro-hydrogen system for coping with renewable energy fluctuation, and providing reference for researches such as system planning configuration and operation optimization related to the electro-hydrogen flexibility."
                },
                {
                    "p": "一种考虑时空表现的电氢系统灵活性测度方法，包括：(1)电氢系统灵活资源研究，依次从灵活性资源整合、规划配置、运行调控、量化评估方法四个方面总结了电氢灵活性的现有研究；(2)针对电氢系统中不确定性，分析系统灵活性来源；(3)基于电氢系统输出特性、功率调节等特性，挖掘系统中储能、变流器、电解槽和辅机等子单元在不同时空尺度上的可调灵活性资源，提出“时间‑空间‑表现”的三维灵活性测度体系，进行电氢系统灵活性量化分析；(4)构建统灵活性测度函数，刻画电氢子系统的灵活性大小，评估电氢系统中各子系统应对可再生能源波动的灵活调节潜力，为电氢灵活性相关的系统规划配置和运行优化等研究提供参考。"
                }
            ]
